{"id": 382, "genre": 1001, "title": "你最烦别人怎么过六一？", "description": "这群大儿童哪儿来的？聊你们的大盘去吧，可憋跟这儿装嫩了！", "record_count": 1128, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160607194605yWULtCuqxO0F7DNw.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-06-01T00:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 2438, "content": "没了儿童命，还有孩子病。", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 113508}, {"id": 2475, "content": "吐槽自己年龄有多大 其实也才20来岁…", "image": "img/option/option/201606042348557GCKABXuIjwFxyVD.jpg", "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 117023}, {"id": 2484, "content": "老师有男朋友啦！", "image": "img/option/option/20160604234716Ae9T6KwIgJnNZWcP.jpg", "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118050}, {"id": 2930, "content": "一不给礼物，二不请吃东西，三还带骂人打人训人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 133734}, {"id": 2581, "content": "一把年纪还到处要六一礼物", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 126299}, {"id": 7709, "content": "晒自己装萌的自拍还附赠一张自己买的零食并说身边没人自己给自己过六一。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 158342}, {"id": 2619, "content": "人山人海过六一是最烦的…", "image": "img/option/option/201606042347135HVqd0hLIX9wPaQ1.jpg", "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 125305}, {"id": 2399, "content": "晒自己的（还是很丑的）童年照片", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193924BoYOHDNbzPSCp0vU.jpg", "praise_count": 96, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 2400, "content": "晒自己的自拍还嘟嘴，吓死个人", "image": "img/option/option/201606052118266NKL5VvpblAGCXkW.jpg", "praise_count": 149, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 2401, "content": "无休止地在各种节日秀恩爱虐狗", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211826E0FXzPL64rsU9bBi.jpg", "praise_count": 84, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 2402, "content": "上社交网络要礼物，能再缺爱一点吗", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193924z6mvUnhCjEtlFKqx.jpg", "praise_count"